name: The Force Unleashed
Text: 'Deploy on table. During battle, you may play Lightsaber Parry, Tarkin''s Orders, and There Is No Conflict as follows: ''If Vader or Galen present: USED: Target a vehicle or starship present. Draw destiny. If destiny > 2, target ''thrown'' (hit and adds its printed defense value to your total power). LOST: Target opponent''s character present and choose (then draw destiny): If destiny > ability, target ''choked'' (lost). OR If destiny +1 > ability, target ''drained of life'' (hit and opponent loses 2 Force).''(Errata Text - September 9th, 2009)',
